flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[User visits App]
    B --> C{Already have an account?}
    
    C -->|No| D[Sign Up]
    C -->|Yes| E[Log In]
    
    D --> F[Go to Dashboard]
    E --> F

    F --> G{What do you want to do?}

    G -->|Add Expenses| H[Add Expense Manually\nor Upload CSV File]
    G -->|View Reports| M[View Dashboard & Analytics]
    G -->|Check Alerts| P[View Suspicious Transactions]

    H --> I{Expenses Added Successfully?}
    I -->|No - Error| J[Show Validation Error\nAsk User to Fix]
    J --> H
    I -->|Yes| K[Expenses Saved]
    K --> L[Auto-categorized &\nRisk Scored in Background]
    L --> F

    M --> N[See Spending by Category\nForecast vs Actual\nOverspending Risk Level]
    N --> O{Need to filter?}
    O -->|Yes| O1[Filter by Date / Category / Risk]
    O1 --> N
    O -->|No| F

    P --> Q[See Flagged Transactions\nwith Risk Level: Low / Medium / High]
    Q --> R{Take Action?}
    R -->|Mark as Reviewed| S[Transaction Marked Safe]
    R -->|Ignore| F
    S --> F

    F --> T([End / Stay on Dashboard])